text: Labarrère is a former commune in the Gers department. It is in southwestern France. On 1 January 2016, it became a part of the new commune of Castelnau-d'Auzan-Labarrère.Arrêté préfectoral 8 December 2015 == Related pages == * Communes of the Gers department == References == Category:Former communes in Gers
